---
import { profile } from '../data/profile'; const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-slate-200 py-8"><div class="container-shell flex flex-col gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"><p>{profile.handle} · {year}</p><p>Built with Astro and deployed on GitHub Pages.</p></div></footer>
